Flicker/Phoenix::

Flicker awakes just in time to hear Starstorm's signal.  "Phoenix, 
wake up!  Starstorm's in trouble!"

"What?!  Where?"  Phoenix sits bolt upright.  "We've got to help her!"

"Take Pumpskin with you for backup, I just got another notifier from 
Perceptor."

Phoenix transforms to beast mode and flies out of Flicker's quarters, 
stopping only long enough to rouse the local basket case and tell him 
of the situation.  With the octolantern in tow, Phoenix flies out to 
Starstorm's position.
